tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE game_event_logs (
  event_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  player_id INT,
  action VARCHAR(255),
  item_id INT,
  game_outcome VARCHAR(255),
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE game_events (
    event_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    player_id INT,
    event_type VARCHAR(50),
    event_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    event_details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE player_actions (
    action_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    player_id INT,
    action_type VARCHAR(50),
    action_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    action_details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE item_interactions (
    interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    player_id INT,
    item_id INT,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE game_outcomes (
    outcome_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    player_id INT,
    game_result VARCHAR(50),
    outcome_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    outcome_details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE player_actions (
    action_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    player_id INT,
    action_type VARCHAR(50),
    action_description TEXT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE item_interactions (
    interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    player_id INT,
    item_id INT,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    interaction_description TEXT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE game_outcomes (
    outcome_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    game_id INT,
    outcome_description TEXT,
    winner_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE players (
    player_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    player_name VARCHAR(50),
    join_date DATE,
    num_games_played INT,
    last_game_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
